{
  "texts": [
    "CIFAR-10 has 60,000 images with 10 classes, CIFAR-100 has 60,000 images with 100 classes, and the ImageNet data set consist 1.2 million images with 1000 classes.",
    "These data sets collected from academic and research institutions.",
    "It has a few thousand to more than a million images.The data set used and the number of layers in the model influenced how accurate these models were.",
    "On the ImageNet data set, VGG accuracy is 92.7% while Inception had an accuracy of 95.2%.",
    "On the ImageNet data set, ResNet achieved an accuracy of 96.54% [2]."
  ]
}